006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item.atomic;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.impl.AbstractStringMapKey;
009import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.metapath.item.function.IMapKey;
010
011import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
012
013public abstract class AbstractStringItem
014    extends AbstractAnyAtomicItem<String>
015    implements IStringItem {
016
017  /**
018   * Construct a new string item with the provided {@code value}.
019   *
020   * @param value
021   *          the value to wrap
022   */
023  protected AbstractStringItem(@NonNull String value) {
024    super(value);
025  }
026
027  @Override
028  public String asString() {
029    return getValue();
030  }
031
032  @Override
033  public IMapKey asMapKey() {
034    return new MapKey();
035  }
036
037  @Override
038  public int hashCode() {
039    return asString().hashCode();
040  }
041
042  @SuppressWarnings("PMD.OnlyOneReturn")
043  @Override
044  public boolean equals(Object obj) {
045    return this == obj
046        || (obj instanceof IStringItem && compareTo((IStringItem) obj) == 0);
047  }
048
049  private final class MapKey
050      extends AbstractStringMapKey {
051
052    @Override
053    public IStringItem getKey() {
054      return AbstractStringItem.this;
055    }
056  }
057}
